name: Autobird - Flappy duck
description:
This is not your average flappy bird clone! This is our DarkHunt duck combined with time wasting clicking game! :)

Will you be able to find optimal balance between manually tapping and flapping and upgrading the duck so it can fly all by itself? Gaining high score is tricky, you pay for your upgrades by the Flaps score so choose wisely :).

Android version: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.playito.autobird
